trans-unit.source: An abstract base class that implements the <xref:System.IAsyncResult> interface.
trans-unit.target: En abstrakt basisklasse som implementerer den <xref:System.IAsyncResult>grensesnittet.</xref:System.IAsyncResult>

trans-unit.source: Serves as a base class from which to derive <xref:System.IAsyncResult> objects that can be used for common asynchronous programming scenarios.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som en basisklasse som avledes <xref:System.IAsyncResult>objekter som kan brukes for vanlige asynkrone programming scenarier.</xref:System.IAsyncResult>

trans-unit.source: For more information see the <xref:System.IAsyncResult?displayProperty=fullName> interface.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon, kan du se den <xref:System.IAsyncResult?displayProperty=fullName>grensesnittet.</xref:System.IAsyncResult?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IdentityModel.TypedAsyncResult%601>for å forhindre AsyncResult.</xref:System.IdentityModel.TypedAsyncResult%601>
